.TH EYE_MOUSE_X11 1

.SH NAME
eye_mouse_x11 \- Tobii eye tracking mouse controller for X11

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B eye_mouse_x11

.SH DESCRIPTION
Eye controlled mouse cursor for X11 using Tobii eye trackers.

Requires a calibration file generated by:

.B calibration_x11

Features:
.IP
- barycentric mesh warp
.IP
- adaptive edge learning
.IP
- smoothing
.IP
- dynamic resolution
.IP
- standalone operation

.SH FILES
.TP
.B ~/.local/tobii_4c/calx11.conf
Calibration mesh configuration.

.SH AUTHOR
Uwe Niethammer
